---
title: Italian Cheesy Chicken Burger & Beetroot Relish with Veggie Fries
description: Bring a little Italian flair to burger night by using classic flavours such as beetroot, Italian herbs, Parmesan and dill-parsley mayo
to turn a tender chicken fillet into a filling supreme burger.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/italian-cheesy-chicken-burger-caramelised-onion-1f164b7e.jpg
